nexus setup 
1. Nexus Installation (Amazon Linux 2023)
sudo useradd nexus

cd /opt

sudo wget https://cdn.download.sonatype.com/repository/downloads-prod-group/3/nexus-3.93.1-04-linux-x86_64.tar.gz

sudo tar -xzf nexus-3.93.1-04-linux-x86_64.tar.gz

sudo mv nexus-3.93.1-04 nexus

sudo chown -R nexus:nexus /opt/nexus
2. Configure Nexus user
sudo vi /opt/nexus/bin/nexus.rc

Add:

run_as_user="nexus"
3. Create Nexus service
sudo vi /etc/systemd/system/nexus.service

Content:

[Unit]
Description=Nexus Repository Manager
After=network.target

[Service]
Type=simple
User=nexus
Group=nexus
LimitNOFILE=65536
ExecStart=/opt/nexus/bin/nexus run
ExecStop=/bin/kill -15 $MAINPID
Restart=on-failure
TimeoutSec=600

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
4. Start Nexus
sudo systemctl daemon-reload

sudo systemctl enable nexus

sudo systemctl start nexus

sudo systemctl status nexus

Check:

curl http://localhost:8081
5. First login

Browser:

http://SERVER-IP:8081

Username:

admin

Initial password:

cat /opt/sonatype-work/nexus3/admin.password

First login తర్వాత కొత్త password set చేయండి.

6. Create Maven Repository

Nexus UI:

Administration
    ↓
Repositories
    ↓
Create repository
    ↓
maven2 (hosted)

Name:

maven-release

Deployment policy:

Allow redeploy

Create.

7. Jenkins Agent Maven settings

Jenkins user:

sudo su - jenkins

mkdir -p ~/.m2

vi ~/.m2/settings.xml

Add:

<settings>
    <servers>
        <server>
            <id>nexus</id>
            <username>admin</username>
            <password>YourPassword</password>
        </server>
    </servers>
</settings>
